        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[大家早安，周末愉快[太阳]早餐科普时间到！[疑问]豆浆和鸡蛋一起吃，会消化不良？鸡蛋中的蛋白质和豆浆里的胰蛋白酶在结合时会产生沉淀，增加消化不良的可能性。...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[大家早安，周末愉快<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[太阳]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/w_taiyang-2b1d91ddac.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>早餐科普时间到！<br><br><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[疑问]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yiwen-40c066d5c3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>豆浆和鸡蛋一起吃，会消化不良？<br><br>鸡蛋中的蛋白质和豆浆里的胰蛋白酶在结合时会产生沉淀，增加消化不良的可能性。但是豆浆在烹饪过程中，里面的胰蛋白酶会被高温分解，根本没有与蛋白质结合的机会，所以，放心吃！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>小卫提醒，豆浆一定要彻底煮熟，喝下不熟的豆浆，可能会引起头晕、腹泻、呕吐，甚至中毒等症状！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（科学辟谣）<br><br>（再问问大家，今天有什么安排<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hkf7tskaaqj20sg0sggo8.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
